---
// In-article newsletter CTA
// Uses Mailchimp signup URL from existing youtube-bot config
---

<aside class="inline-signup" aria-label="Suscripcion newsletter">
  <div class="inline-signup__content">
    <h3>Recibe tips de salud cada domingo</h3>
    <p>Unete a nuestra newsletter gratuita. Consejos practicos basados en ciencia, directo a tu email.</p>
    <a
      href="http://eepurl.com/c_iwJy-3pL"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener"
      class="btn btn--primary"
    >
      Suscribirme gratis
    </a>
  </div>
</aside>

<style>
  .inline-signup {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FFF5F5 0%, #FEF2F2 100%);
    border: 1px solid #FECACA;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 2rem;
    margin: 2.5rem 0;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .inline-signup h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .inline-signup p {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    max-width: 480px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }
</style>
